skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ready set know
des:
Ready Set Know is a trivia game that tests your ability to recognize a pattern, rather than knowing a fact. Items of a set will be read to you one at a time, all you need to do is figure out what comes next. Ready Set Know offers multiple difficulties, as well as a variety of genres for the sequences. 
Ready? Listen to some things from the Set. And tell Alexa when you Know the what comes next!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
